      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the whole company, the funding, all of it. i just sat in my office for three hours staring at the empty desks. i have no way to pay back the investors and if i go back home my parents and everyone will just look at me like i'm a joke. i can't do it. i literally can't face them.",
