    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just \"overwhelmed\" though. it's like... there's no coming back from this. if i go back, i have to explain the debt and the mess i made to everyone who believed in me. the shame is actually physically painful. i feel like there's no Version 2.0 of me. there's just the version that failed everything.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
