      "content": "Failure is often just a single chapter, not the entire story, and many individuals discover that new skills and perspectives bloom from such intense emotional chapters. The pain you feel is a sign of your deep investment and care, not proof that you are permanently broken; your value as a person remains untouched by business setbacks. Please reach out to a therapist who can help you untangle these feelings of shame so you can find hope again for a future beyond this specific moment.",
      "source": "target",
